sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMES Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Job as Job Pod<br/>(ta-lmes-job container)<br/>User: 65532
    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GPU as Local GPU/CPU<br/>(in-process)
    participant Output as Output PVC / S3<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RemoteAPI as Remote API Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Operator,Output: Flow 1: Local Model Evaluation Job

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job resource<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Job created

    activate Job
    Job->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM credentials (env vars)
    S3-->>Job: Model weights & data

    Job->>HFHub: Download tokenizer & datasets<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>HF Token (optional)
    HFHub-->>Job: Tokenizer, datasets

    Job->>GPU: Load model & run evaluation<br/>In-process<br/>No network
    GPU-->>Job: Inference results

    Job->>Output: Write evaluation results<br/>Filesystem (PVC) or<br/>HTTPS/443 (S3)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    deactivate Job

    Note over Job,RemoteAPI: Flow 2: Remote API Model Evaluation

    activate Job
    Job->>RemoteAPI: Model inference request<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>API Key (Bearer)
    RemoteAPI-->>Job: Inference response

    Job->>Output: Write evaluation results<br/>Filesystem (PVC) or<br/>HTTPS/443 (S3)
    deactivate Job
